    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a perfect balance of performance and pride of ownership. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that still catches the light beautifully, the exterior shows only the minor, honest signs of careful road use, such as light stone chips on the front fascia. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary; the leather seats remain supple with minimal bolstering wear, and every electronic component\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. I have maintained a meticulous service folder, including a recent synthetic oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection that confirmed the engine and transmission are pulling smoothly. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. If you are looking for a reliable, aesthetically pleasing driver that has been treated with respect rather than just driven, this is the one.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
